data.description: Looking for wide open spaces? Your new home offers tons of space, inside and out. Within your beautiful 3456 sq/ft steel structured farm house you'll find 4 huge bedrooms, a spacious eat-in kitchen, a large open living room, and a giant loft that makes a perfect game room, work out space, art studio...you name it! You'll love all the efficient features of your home, like the recirculating water heater, the wood stove w/blower, LED light fixtures, 2 yo appliances and the solar panels, all of which significantly trim utility costs! Each detail is designed with ease of maintenance in mind, like the gorgeous mudroom with a floor drain for easy clean up and laminate/tile floors! Working from home is a breeze with fiber optic internet, too! Outside, find 10 acres of nature to be explored as well as a 1500 sq/ft barn with water and electric, so you can hook up your RV.  All of this is convenient to Springdale, Rogers, Fayetteville and Eureka Springs, but you have 1 sweet neighbor to loan you sugar to save a trip to town.
